features: Includes 60 Sheets: Enjoy 60 sheets of beautifully crafted 8.5" x 11" decorative letterhead. Each sheet is a canvas for your holiday messages.
Standard Size, Easy Sending: Designed to fit seamlessly into standard #10 or A9 envelopes, our letter size paper is a breeze to print and send.

Printer Friendly Quality: Our high-quality , 90 GSM paper is printer-friendly and compatible with most home or office printers. Whether for business or personal use, your printing experience will be seamless.

Uniquely Festive Designs: Get into the holiday spirit with our Christmas & Holiday-themed designs. Each sheet exudes the joyful essence of the season, perfect for spreading cheer to your Christmas list recipients.

Versatile Use: Let your creativity flow as you write or print your holiday letters, heartfelt thank-yous, or new year greetings on our charming snowman at play design. It adds a touch of charm to every message you send.

Elevate Your Holiday Correspondence Festive Flair in Every Word: Christmas Letterheads - Pack of 60 Unveil the magic of the season with our Christmas Letterhead Pack of 60. Each sheet, meticulously designed and sized perfectly at 8.5 x 11 inches (A4), sets the stage for your heartfelt holiday messages. With six versatile designs, you have the ideal canvas to express warm wishes, gratitude, and festive cheer. Whether for business greetings or personal notes, make every word count with this exquisite collection. Seasonal Elegance, 60 Times Over Christmas Letterheads: 60-Piece Pack, A4 Size - 8.5 x 11 Inches Indulge in the spirit of the holidays with our Christmas Letterhead Pack, a harmonious blend of style and substance. With 60 meticulously crafted sheets in A4 size (8.5 x 11 inches), each piece radiates seasonal elegance. Choose from six versatile designs to make your letters and greetings stand out, creating a lasting impression during this joyous time of the year. Effortless Elegance for Your Words Easy-to-Write Letterheads: Simplifying Your Correspondence Discover the joy of seamless expression with our Easy-to-Write Letterheads. The perfect canvas for your thoughts, each sheet invites you to convey your messages effortlessly. Sized conveniently at 8.5 x 11 inches, these letterheads are designed for simplicity without compromising style. Elevate your writing experience with our thoughtfully crafted collection, making every letter a breeze and a pleasure to write.
